TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT APPL.SLS_CREDIT_ASGNMT_SLS_TRX_KEY , APPL.SO_SBSCRPTN_ITM_SLS_TRX_KEY , APPL.BK_OFFER_ATTRIBUTION_ID_INT , APPL.BK_ATTRIBUTION_SS_CD , APPL.BK_SLS_TERR_ASSIGNMENT_TYPE_CD, APPL.ATTR_PRDT_AS_NEW_OR_RNWL_KEY , APPL.SALES_CREDIT_USAGE_CD , APPL.SALES_CREDIT_UNALLOCATED_FLG , APPL.SLS_CREDIT_ASGNMT_MODE_CD , APPL.SK_TRX_SPLIT_SC_ID_INT , APPL.OVERLAY_TYPE , APPL.BK_SALES_REP_NUM , APPL.BK_SLS_TERR_ASGNMT_TYPE_CD , APPL.SALES_TERRITORY_KEY , APPL.SRC_RPTD_REBOK_OTM_TERR_ID_INT, APPL.SRC_RPTD_REBOK_OTM_TERR_NAME , APPL.SRC_RPTD_REBOK_OTM_TERR_TYP_CD, APPL.BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CODE , APPL.BK_CREATED_BY_ERP_USER_NAME , APPL.BK_SLS_CRDT_ASGNMT_RSN_CD , APPL.SCA_CREATE_DTM , APPL.DV_SCA_CREATE_DT , APPL.SCA_LAST_UPDATE_DTM , APPL.DV_SCA_LAST_UPDATE_DT , APPL.SPLIT_PCT , APPL.EFFECTIVE_START_DTM , APPL.DV_EFFECTIVE_START_DT , APPL.EFFECTIVE_END_DTM , APPL.DV_EFFECTIVE_END_DT , APPL.SOURCE_COMMIT_DTM , APPL.DV_SOURCE_COMMIT_DT , APPL.UCRM_CASE_NUM , APPL.BK_TRX_SPLIT_BU_ID , APPL.SK_TRX_SPLIT_ID_INT , APPL.SALES_MOTION_CD , APPL.SK_RTR_ATTRIBUTION_ID , APPL.SPLIT_1_OFFER_ATTRIBITION_PCT , APPL.SPLIT_2_NEW_RENEW_PCT , APPL.TOTAL_SPLIT_PCT , APPL.RU_REBOK_CHANNEL_FLG , APPL.EDW_CREATE_DTM , APPL.EDW_CREATE_USER , APPL.EDW_UPDATE_DTM , APPL.EDW_UPDATE_USER , APPL.START_TV_DTM , APPL.END_TV_DTM , APPL.SBSCRPTN_ITEM_CHANGE_ID_INT AS SBSCRPTN_ITEM_CHANGE_ID_INT , APPL.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY AS AR_TRX_LINE_KEY , APPL.ACTION_CD , NSCTT.SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_QUOTA_FLAG AS QUOTA_FLAG , /* NFISMN_SYS IS USEFUL WHEN NET CHANGE RUNS FOR CATCHUP DATA (OR BACKDATING AND RUNNING NET CHANGE PART) */ CASE WHEN ( NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100 ) < (NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100) THEN NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT ELSE NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT END AS BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT , CASE WHEN ( NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100 ) < (NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100) THEN NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT ELSE NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT END AS BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT , CASE WHEN ( NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100 ) < (NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100) THEN (NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN_SYS.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100) ELSE ( NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT+NFISMN.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT *100 ) END AS DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MONTH_NUM_INT FROM (SELECT LAST_EXTRACT_DATE FROM $$ETLVWDB.DW_JOB_STREAMS WHERE JOB_STREAM_ID ='Wf_WI_REV_SCA_NRT_XAAS_SMR_TV') X, ( SELECT BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT, BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT FROM $$COMREFVWDB.N_FISCAL_MONTH WHERE CURRENT_DATE-1 BETWEEN FISCAL_MONTH_START_DATE AND FISCAL_MONTH_END_DATE ) NFISMN_SYS , $$STGDB.WI_REV_SCA_NRT_SNAP_XAAS_SMR APPL LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CODE, SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_QUOTA_FLAG FROM $$SLSORDVWDB.N_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_TV QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER () OVER (PARTITION BY BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CODE ORDER BY END_TV_DATE DESC)=1 ) NSCTT ON APPL.BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CODE = NSCTT.BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CODE
INNER JOIN $$COMREFVWDB.N_FISCAL_MONTH NFISMN ON APPL.SOURCE_COMMIT_DTM BETWEEN NFISMN.FISCAL_MONTH_START_DATE AND NFISMN.FISCAL_MONTH_END_DATE WHERE 1=1 /* TO PULL INCREMENTALLY */ AND APPL.EDW_UPDATE_DTM > X.LAST_EXTRACT_DATE AND NOT /* NOT TO TAKE RETRO UPDATES */ ( APPL.EDW_CREATE_DTM <= X.LAST_EXTRACT_DATE /* OLD CREATED */ AND EFFECTIVE_END_DTM = '3500-01-01 00:00:00' /* OPEN RECORD */ ) AND NOT EXISTS ( SEL 1 FROM $$STGDB.WI_REV_SCA_NRT_XAAS_SMR_INCR_PRE PRE WHERE APPL.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY=PRE.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY AND APPL.SALES_TERRITORY_KEY=PRE.SALES_TERRITORY_KEY AND APPL.BK_SALES_REP_NUM=PRE.BK_SALES_REP_NUM AND APPL.SK_RTR_ATTRIBUTION_ID=PRE.SK_RTR_ATTRIBUTION_ID AND APPL.BK_OFFER_ATTRIBUTION_ID_INT =PRE.BK_OFFER_ATTRIBUTION_ID_INT AND APPL.TOTAL_SPLIT_PCT =PRE.TOTAL_SPLIT_PCT AND APPL.SALES_MOTION_CD =PRE.SALES_MOTION_CD )

APPL.BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CODE , APPL.BK_CREATED_BY_ERP_USER_NAME , APPL.BK_SLS_CRDT_ASGNMT_RSN_CD , APPL.SCA_CREATE_DTM , APPL.DV_SCA_CREATE_DT , APPL.SCA_LAST_UPDATE_DTM , APPL.DV_SCA_LAST_UPDATE_DT , APPL.SPLIT_PCT , APPL.EFFECTIVE_START_DTM , APPL.DV_EFFECTIVE_START_DT , APPL.EFFECTIVE_END_DTM , APPL.DV_EFFECTIVE_END_DT , APPL.SOURCE_COMMIT_DTM , APPL.DV_SOURCE_COMMIT_DT , APPL.UCRM_CASE_NUM , APPL.BK_TRX_SPLIT_BU_ID , APPL.SK_TRX_SPLIT_ID_INT , APPL.SALES_MOTION_CD , APPL.SK_RTR_ATTRIBUTION_ID , APPL.SPLIT_1_OFFER_ATTRIBITION_PCT , APPL.SPLIT_2_NEW_RENEW_PCT , APPL.TOTAL_SPLIT_PCT , APPL.RU_REBOK_CHANNEL_FLG , APPL.EDW_CREATE_DTM , APPL.EDW_CREATE_USER , APPL.EDW_UPDATE_DTM , APPL.EDW_UPDATE_USER , APPL.START_TV_DTM , APPL.END_TV_DTM , APPL.SBSCRPTN_ITEM_CHANGE_ID_INT AS SBSCRPTN_ITEM_CHANGE_ID_INT , APPL.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY AS AR_TRX_LINE_KEY , APPL.ACTION_CD , APPL.QUOTA_FLAG, APPL.BK_FISCAL_MONTH_NUMBER_INT , APPL.BK_FISCAL_YEAR_NUMBER_INT , APPL.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MONTH_NUM_INT FROM $$STGDB.WI_REV_SCA_NRT_XAAS_SMR_INCR APPL WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE DRVD INNER JOIN $$FINLGLVWDB.N_AR_TRX_LINE NATL ON DRVD.DV_AR_TRX_LINE_KEY = NATL.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY INNER JOIN $$FINLGLVWDB.N_AR_TRX NAT ON NATL.AR_TRX_KEY=NAT.AR_TRX_KEY INNER JOIN $$FINLGLVWDB.N_AR_BATCH_SOURCE NABS ON NAT.AR_BATCH_SOURCE_KEY = NABS.AR_BATCH_SOURCE_KEY WHERE NATL.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY=APPL.AR_TRX_LINE_KEY AND NABS.BK_BATCH_SOURCE_NAME LIKE ANY ('ICMS-XAAS%','PP-XAAS%','XAAS%','CSP-MARKETPLACE')/*ADDED AS PART OF Q1FY19 CE-BRAZIL*/ )
